title: Vote Por Zombozo
description: Cuando el Chatarra debe ponerse a punto en la misma ciudad por donde pasa la campaña de Zombozo, Ben pronto descubre que el payaso usa sus discursos para hipnotizar al pueblo y robarse sus pertenencias. El equipo Tennyson debe impedir que el villano gane las elecciones.

title: I……am Vampier
description: When Vic enters the Monte Macabre film festival, he gets insecure about his artistic vision and decides to copy the work of others, but ultimately learns that staying true to yourself is what's most important.

title: Worship
description: When the Fashionistas unveil their new mind controlling perfume, the Powerpuff Girls must find a way to stop them before Townsville falls under their spell.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The New Crystal Gems
description: Connie helps look after Beach City while Steven is busy.

title: Schnorp
description: The Thunderkittens plug a new video game cartridge into Snarf only to learn that it didn't load a game, it loaded a whole new personality into their pal! Meet Schnorp, a kind Swedish man who loves the beauty of nature and collecting berries! Schnorp is loads of fun, but we're gonna want Snarf back, right?

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Drawn to Sports with Zachary
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Zachary loves competing and developing his skills in karate.

title: Emergency
description: When Grizz comes home with a live crab, he thinks it can become a pet for the brothers to share. However, after the crab pinches Ice Bear's ear and won't let go, Panda and Grizz have to get their injured brother to the hospital, and fast!

title: Off Duty Cop
description: Daffy impersonates his favorite 70s detective show star.

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Prepare for the Worst
description: Axel and Bobbie Blobby skip out on Sarge's disaster-prep drills, leaving enough of a gap in the team's defenses for a crow to swoop in and snatch Sarge! Feeling responsible, Axel leads the team on a search-and-rescue mission.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Emergencia
description: Cuando Pardo llega a su casa con un cangrejo vivo, piensa que el cangrejo puede ser una mascota para los tres hermanos. Sin embargo, cuando el cangrejo le pellizca la oreja a Polar y no lo suelta, Panda y Pardo tienen que llevar a su hermano lastimado al hospital, ide inmediato!

title: The Kindergarten Kid
description: Steven and the Gems deal with a monster problem.

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 1
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Aquarium for a Dream
description: Gwen tries to convince Chef to tell the class the truth about their pet goldfish.

title: Flyaway
description: When Adorabat's spirit transcends her body during a meditation exercise, Mao Mao and Badgerclops have to figure out a way to return her to the real world.

title: El regreso de Xingo
description: Cuando Ben debe divertirse solo durante la merecida siesta de Max, se topa con un juego de Xingo y decide convertirse en OE-Shock Rock para encenderlo. Pero cuando Xingo recibe demasiada carga, salta al mundo real, y nuestro héroe debe quedar frente a frente con su personaje animado favorito.

title: The 11th Alien Part 2
description: After discovering that Vilgax has joined forces with the Weatherheads to trick him into turning over the Omnitrix, Ben must not only overcome his doubts, but fully embrace his new powers if he is to beat his foes.

title: The Sound and the Furry
description: As Team Tennyson leaves the Frozen Man Festival, Lord Decibel takes center stage to threaten the festival-goers, creating an avalanche if his ransom isn't paid. An over matched Ben must step out of his comfort zone to save the festival from his noisy nemesis!

title: Fire Maker
description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: El Hacedor de Fuego
description: El Emperador de Hielo se entera de la llegada de los ninjas y envía a sus guerreros Samurais Blizzard a destruirlos, y a todos los aldeanos que los albergaron.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Paste Makes Waste/Ice Sore
description: Paste Makes Waste: When Buttercup's taunting turns paste-eating classmate Elmer Sglue into a destructive Paste Monster, she gets out of a sticky situation by doing something against her tough nature, apologizing./Ice Sore: During a heat wave, Blossom discovers that she has a new power: ice breath. But when she doesn't use her new gift wisely, she gets a chilly reception from her sisters.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: The Return
description: Dad is in charge of getting the kids to their first day back at school on time, but he's overslept and now he can't find Gumball, Darwin or Anais anywhere. He sets about retracing his steps from the day before to work out where they might be.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: The Visitor
description: A vision leads Finn to a friendly civilization and a mysterious crash site.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The 11th Alien Part 1
description: With new Omni-Enhancements in tow, Ben looks to save a town from a sudden mudslide, but his heroics are short lived once Vilgax appears to warn our hero about the consequences of the Omnitrix's mysterious new alien.

title: Uncle Grandpa at the Movies
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve cause a ruckus at the movies, Mr. Gus is forced to play the hero in order to save the day.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: La cita
description: Cuando Chef está feliz ordena pizza para los niños. Esto le da a Owen & Jude la idea de crear una falsa admiradora secreta para Chef.

title: El Camino
description: iEste episodio transcurre cuando los Osos son cachorritos! Los tres Osos, en su viaje por el desierto, se topan con un depósito gigante. Los Osos tratan de convertir este paraíso repleto de cajas en su hogar.

title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Weapon XI Part 2
description: The Rooters have seemingly turned Kevin and the Amalgam kids against Ben. Can Rook and Gwen help him overcome the opposition and escape the Null Void?

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: #SoulSisters Part 1
description: The girls must track down Katana, a mysterious warrior who's stealing the souls of Metropolis's villains. Meanwhile, Diana's new friend Tatsu is a perfect match for her in every way, but may have a connection to Katana.

title: Winner Takes All
description: After months of training for Luchador Day, Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo!

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Ganas de Explorar
description: La misión de Craig de mapear el Arroyo entero los lleva a él y a sus amigos a arboleda traicionera de Hiedra Venenosa
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Vote Zombozo!
description: When the Rustbucket must tune-up in the same town as Zombozo's latest campaign trail stop, Ben soon discovers the clown is using his speeches to hypnotize then rob the town, and Team Tennyson must stop the baddie from winning the election.

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 1
description: Con sus nuevas Omni-Mejoras, Ben intenta salvar una ciudad de un repentino alud. Pero su heroísmo dura poco, porque llega Vilgax a advertirlo de las consecuencias del misterioso alien del Omnitrix.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Sunday Night Slice
description: When Bugs' favorite pizza place closes, he takes matters into his own hands.

title: Hot Dog Estrena su Pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: P.L.O.T. Device 2: Beyond the Bored Dome
description: Dr. Fox reprograms the P.L.O.T. Device to only generate boring events, but the gang can't help but add drama and excitement to every scenario.

title: El Mensaje
description: Lloyd y su compañero lobo encuentran una cueva y encuentran al Mech adentro. Escuchan un mensaje de Zane que les da una pista de su destino.

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: The Pest
description: When they find Anais training herself for a brutal showdown, Gumball and Darwin realize their sister is being pestered at school by an annoying kid, Billy. They try to teach her how to resolve the problem peacefully but Billy has other ideas.

title: Sir Tree's Body
description: Seth wants to help sad, immobile Sir Tree feel the joy that comes from helping others, so he has the brilliant idea of planting Sir Tree inside Pascal's body! But when Sir Tree's absence causes soil erosion and mudslides, Seth has to convince Sir Tree that the best way to help is to return to his hole before Fancytown is destroyed.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ruidosos y Peludos
description: Cuando los Tennyson se van del Festival Frozen Man, Lord Decibel ocupa el escenario central para amenazar a los asistentes y crear una avalancha si no pagan el rescate que pide. iBen se ve superado por su rival y debe salir de su zona de confort para salvar al festival de su entrometido enemigo!

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Suelta
description: Cuando el espíritu de Adorabat trasciende su cuerpo durante un ejercicio de meditación, Mao Mao y Colosal tienen que descubrir un modo de devolverla al mundo real.

title: Memory Mayhem
description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Desde las Profundidades
description: iAxel hace malabares cuidando a Luka y defendiendo la casa de la última abominación del Dr. Nautilus, un monstruo tentáculo que ataca desde cada drenaje, tubería y grifo del edificio!

title: Smile Bones
description: When Cyborg and Beast Boy teach the other Titans to wolf down their food, the gang develops a big fat problem.

title: Walnuts & Rain
description: Finn & Jake stumble into two different holes and meet two different fates.

title: Chip's Damage
description: Elodie enlists KO to help figure out what to do about Chip Damage.

title: Say Hello to my Little Friends
description: After telling the kids he will not miss them over the long weekend Chef locks himself into the school and finds out he was very, very wrong.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Whatever Happened to... Rippy Roo?
description: Rippy Roo visits the plaza.

title: Water Park
description: The trio heads to Squirty's Moist Mountain water park, and as Clarence learns the truth about his idol Squirty, Jeff and Sumo wait in line for the reopening of the parks tallest slide, The Curd Churner.

title: Ropa Dominguera
description: JP ensucia su última ropa limpia y debe ponerse su mejor ropa de domingo para ir al arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: You Forgot Your Floaties
description: Finn and Jake storm Magic Man's house to rescue his new apprentice.

title: #AmiEnemigas - Segunda Parte
description: Los mundos de Batgirl colisionan cuando su mejor amiga de Gotham City se muda a Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Catwoman también hace nuevos amigos...
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Charlie and the Snake
description: Charlie is a solo guy who, like the Bears, would love to find a place for himself in the world. In an effort to do so, Charlie throws a party, but ends up going on an adventure with the unlikeliest of animals, a wild snake.

title: That's My Baby
description: Daffy gets roped into babysitting.

title: Too Far
description: Amethyst and Steven get in on some Gem gossip.

title: Balance
description: Ms. Baker introduces a new student, a short little kid with a hook for a hand named Balance. Clarence is pumped to have a new friend, despite Balance's gruff attitude and snarky jibes at the other kids. When Clarence discovers a disturbing secret about Balance, he and Belson team up to expose him for who he truly is.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 2
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Stretched Too Thin
description: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

title: Victor the Predictor
description: When Victor becomes convinced he has a special talent as a psychic, he decides to use his new mental abilities to counsel those around him - until one piece of advice goes too far.

title: The Best VHS in the World
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to return an overdue VHS to the store so they won't be banned from renting new movies.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: Water Park Prank
description: After rescuing Princess Orangutan from Daddy-sad-heads, Finn and Jake head to a post-apocalyptic water park for a day of fun.

title: Working Duck
description: When Daffy gets fired for sleeping on the job, Bugs kicks him out of the house.

title: Universe vs. Tennyson
description: Ben gets dragged into intergalactic court by the other Celestialsapiens (Alien Xs) for recreating the universe (back in "So Long and Thanks for All the Smoothies").

title: Xingo's Back
description: Left to entertain himself as Max takes a much deserved nap, Ben stumbles upon a Xingo arcade game and goes OE-Shock Rock to power it up, but when it receives too much juice, Xingo leaps out into the real world and our hero must go toe-to-toe with his favorite cartoon character.

title: Baby Caterpillar
description: Unikitty takes in a radioactive caterpillar and raises it like a baby, unaware of the havoc it will wreak as a full-grown adult.

title: Boys vs Girls
description: The Titans try to settle the eternal question: Are boys or girls better?

title: Uncle Baseball
description: A failing little league team on the brink of giving up gets help from Uncle Grandpa and some Major League Baseball players.

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: The Long Skate Home
description: After they get accused of a crime they didn't commit, the Powerpuff girls and the Derbytantes have to find a way to clear their name!

title: El Peor Ninja de Todos
description: De regreso en ciudad Ninjago, tres criminales se enteran de la ausencia de los ninjas y organizan una fuga de la prisión Kryptarium, contando historias sobre cómo fueron capturados mientras avanzaban.

title: Kindred Spirits
description: When Val becomes friends with the ghost of a silent film star, their friendship turns out to have dire consequences.

title: Hachiman
description: While on a super important mission to get batteries for the TV remote Lion-O meets Hachiman, a cool Samurai warrior. Now Lion-O will do anything to prove he's just as cool as Hachiman, even if it means risking his own life!

title: #TheGreenRoom
description: When Jessica is faced with a Green Lantern Corps disciplinary hearing, Hal appoints himself to be her Peer Advocate.

title: Rook Tales
description: Rook's former teacher will preserve Revonnahgander traditions at any cost.

title: #SoulSisters Part 2
description: The girls must track down Katana, a mysterious warrior who's stealing the souls of Metropolis's villains. Meanwhile, Diana's new friend Tatsu is a perfect match for her in every way, but may have a connection to Katana.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Demasiados Tesoros
description: Con la esperanza de reparar su fuerte, Craig consigue la ayuda de Los Veloces Diez para llevarlos hasta la legendaria pila de basura.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Breehn Ho
description: Avast mateys! Clarence and Sumo are psyched to play their pirate-themed board game, Thirty Days and Seven Seas, until they learn Jeff has invited boring old Breehn along. After Breehn gets frustrated and leaves, it's up to the three scallywags to rescue Breehn from an intense flood.

title: Charlie Y La Serpiente
description: Charlie (alias Pie Grande) es un tipo solitario a quien, como a los Osos, le gustaría encontrar un lugar en el mundo. En su intento por conseguirlo, Charlie organiza una fiesta, pero termina embarcándose en una aventura con el más improbable de los animales: una serpiente salvaje.

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: El Estornudo De Panda
description: Los osos panda tienen un estornudo muy adorable (iy violento!), y nuestro Panda no es la excepción. Cuando un video de su estornudo tierno se vuelve viral en la página Vine, Panda se convierte en una sensación ¿tierna¿, lo que hace que Nom Nom trate de ahuyentar a este nuevo contendiente a su trono.

title: The Date
description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

title: The New Nemesis
description: When Hawkodile discovers his old enemy Eagleator has a new nemesis in his life, the gang do all they can to get Hawk back on his foe's radar.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Wake Up
description: In order to find Finn's father, Finn and Jame must commit a cosmic crime unless the Lich beats them to it.

title: TKO Rules!
description: KO and TKO decide to swap places for the day.

title: Cough It Up
description: Psyphon and a gang of bounty hunters are after Argit, who is in possession of a dangerous weapon!

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: The Road
description:
This episode takes place when the Bears are young cubs! The three bears, on their way through the desert, come upon a giant warehouse. It's like an Amazon fulfillment
center. The Bears try to make this box-filled paradise their home.

title: The Message
description: Lloyd and his wolf-companion find a cave with the mech inside and a message from Zane that provides a clue to his fate.

title: The Absolute Worst!
description: Back in Ninjago City, three criminals learn of the ninja's absence and stage a breakout of Kryptarium Prison, telling tall tales of how they were captured as they go.

title: Baost in Show
description: When Bao Bao returns, and the King makes him his pet, Mao Mao must rescue his ex-partner.

title: Trash Boat
description: Rigby changes his name so that he can be cooler.

title: El Reino del Jamas
description: Los ninja llegan al Never-Realm donde rápidamente se sienten abrumados. Afortunadamente, son recibidos por una tribu de pescadores de hielo que les dicen que Zane ha sido encarcelado por el malvado Emperador de hielo.

title: Corporate Buyout
description: The Cheetara Corp employee retreat gets canceled when Baron Karnon, a mysterious corporate raider, buys them out! Now Cheetara and Jan-Jan must brave the wilds of Third Earth's most dangerous jungles to find the Baron's office and demand a meeting with the man who stole their company!

title: Monster in the Garden
description: Craig is determined to catch the monster that has been wreaking havoc in Granddad's garden.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Decoding Valentino
description: When Val goes on an adventure with Isabella to decode an ancient language, he has to come to terms with the fact that Isabella is smarter in order to save himself.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Small World: Stone Cold Spider Part 2
description: With Townsville in peril, the girls are sent to the arctic on a dangerous mission to find the key to saving the day.

title: Stuck on You
description: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Squirrels Squirrels Squirrels
description: Courtney's attempt to make Chef a better teacher fails when a squirrel gets his hands on her mind-control device.

title: DMV
description: Daffy is forced to take a test to get his driver's license after he was discovered driving without one.

title: Mandora's Law
description: Tygra creates a bunch of new laws for Third Earth so Mandora can finally arrest the Mutants. Unfortunately the Thundercats are really bad at following their own rules and the Mutants are really good at working around them.

title: #Frenemies Part 2
description: Batgirl's worlds collide when her best friend from Gotham City moves to Metropolis. Meanwhile, Catwoman is making some new friends of her own.

title: Pain in the Ice/Tunnel Vision/Pool Bunny
description: A hungry Sylvester sets his sights on Tweety the ice skater. On a scorching hot day, Bugs Bunny makes himself at home in Elmer Fudd's pool.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Too Many Treasures
description: Hoping to fix their fort, Craig enlists the 10 Speeds to give them a ride to the legendary Junk Pile.

title: Sunday Clothes
description: JP dirties his last clean clothes and he must wear his Sunday best to the creek.

title: Dawn of the Donut
description: Dr. Fox's plans to deliver donuts all over the Unikingdom are sidetracked by Unikitty's reluctance to follow instructions.

title: Idiosyncratic Induction
description: On Elliott's first day at the Hive, he meets the most unusual characters on his adventure so far.

title: Presumir en el Concurso
description: Cuando Bao Bao regresa y el rey lo convierte en su mascota, Mao Mao debe rescatar a su antiguo compañero.

title: Preparense Para Lo Peor
description: iAxel y Bobbie Blobby se saltan los simulacros de preparación para desastres de Sarge, dejando suficiente espacio en las defensas del equipo para que un cuervo se precipite y arrebata a Sarge! Sintiéndose responsable, Axel lidera al equipo en una misión de búsqueda y rescate.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Monstruo en el Jardin
description: Craig está decidido a atrapar al monstruo que ha estado desatando un caos en el jardín del abuelo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 2
description: Ben descubre que Vilgax se ha unido a los Weatherheads para obligarlo a entregar el Omnitrix. Ahora no solo deberá superar sus dudas, sino también aceptar sus nuevos poderes, si es que quiere derrotar a sus enemigos.

title: Tote Life
description: When a hipster grocery store clerk shames the Bears for asking for plastic grocery bags, the Bears realize that eco-friendly tote bags are their way of gaining acceptance amongst the progressive people of the Bay Area. But in their effort to gain popularity, the Bears let the culture of tote bags take over their lives.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Answer
description: Garnet finally tells Steven the story of how she came to be a Crystal Gem.

title: The Never-Realm
description: The ninja arrive in the Never-Realm where they quickly find themselves overwhelmed. Luckily, they are taken in by a tribe of Ice Fishers who tell them Zane has been imprisoned by the evil Ice Emperor.

title: Thunder Road
description: When a crate containing fifty Swords of Omen lands on Third Earth, the ThunderCats rush out in the ThunderTank to find them. Unfortunately The Mutants and Mumm-Ra want those swords too so it's going to be a race to get to them! A wacky race, you might say. We won't say that, but you might.

title: Panda's Sneeze
description: Panda bears have a very adorable (and violent!) sneeze, and our Panda is no exception. When a Vine video of his very cute sneeze goes viral, Panda becomes a cute sensation, which causes Nom Nom to try to fend off of this new challenger to his throne.

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: An Unlikely Ally
description: Lloyd runs afoul of the Ice Emperor's Blizzard Samurai but is rescued by a strange wolf with whom an unlikely friendship develops.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: Boo! Appetweet/Hole Gag: Plunger/Bubble Dum
description: Sweet victory turns into a nightmare when Sylvester fears he's haunted by Tweety's ghost. Daffy Duck faces off with a pesky piece of gum.

title: Oddities
description: When a mysterious carnival barker fuses V&V together, they must find a way to come unstuck.

title: Play Date
description: Toyman takes over the Justice League and turns them into avatars in a diabolical video game.

title: Trucker Hall of Fame
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to help Muscle Man get to the Big Rig Museum to spread his dad's hat's ashes.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Pretty Great Day with a Girl
description: Clarence and Amy, a unique girl from down the street, bond over a hunt for a monster-sized rock called an "erratic."

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Commander Beefy
description: Seth, eager to explore the stars and find a fellow explorer, sends a signal to space. But the explorer who receives the message, Commander Beefy, has his own shady plans for Earth.

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: #EnterNightSting
description: Karen is given a mission to prevent the apocalypse by DeathSting, a super-cool future version of herself.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: The Points
description: Gumball and Darwin discover Tobias is doing way better than them in an online game called Galatrek. Tobias admits he earns good points doing chores for his parents, which he then exchanges for dollars to buy cool stuff for Galatrek. If Gumball and Darwin do Tobias' chores they can earn his good points and use them for Galatrek. Gumball and Darwin think they've hit the jackpot. But these good points may not be quite as good as Tobias claims.

title: La pecera de los suenos
description: Gwen trata de convencer a Chef de que le diga a la clase la verdad sobre su pececito dorado.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Vida Ecologica
description: Cuando un vendedor moderno en un almacén avergüenza a los Osos por pedir bolsas de plástico, los Osos se dan cuenta de que las bolsas de tela ecológicas son su forma de lograr aceptación entre las personas progresistas del Área de la Bahía. Pero en su esfuerzo por conseguir popularidad, los Osos dejan que la cultura (y la cantidad) de bolsas de tela se apodere de sus vidas.

title: The Recipe
description: Gumball and Darwin discover the secret behind Anton's immortality. Anton's little toasty body disintegrates during a swim class. When Gumball and Darwin see Anton the next day, as good as new, they set out to discover his secret. It turns out that his parents use a special formula to bake new Antons when necessary. So the kids test it out at home and end up baking a clone army whose leader - Ant-one - wants to destroy Anton and take over the world.

title: Straight Illin
description: In an escalating series of dares, Clarence eats five hundred hard-boiled eggs, delighting the kids around him. As Clarence grows sicker and sicker, the kids get more and more grossed out until they want nothing to do with him.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: KO, Rad, and Enid!
description: When confronted with their lack of a team gimmick, KO, Rad, and Enid wonder what their group identity should be.

title: From Below
description: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

title: El Ganador se lo Lleva Todo
description: Después de meses de entrenamiento para el Día del Luchador, Axel necesita que Masko lo entrene contra un par de competidores no invitados: iMadcap y Dynamo!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: The Question
description: Gumball and Darwin seek the answer to the biggest question of all: what is the meaning of life? They need to understand the point of their lives, so resolve to seek advice from everyone in Elmore. They ask people, animals and even planets but their answer comes from an unexpected source.

title: Estirado Demasiado Delgado
description: Después de que un nuevo movimiento combinado deja a Masko permanentemente flácido, Axel y el equipo deben ayudar al luchador caído a recuperarse.

title: Back with a Vengeance
description: Ben's feeling cocky with the watch. He's unlocked its secret, and now can become any alien he wants, whenever he wants. That's the good news. The bad news is, after finding one another in the depths of space, Kevin 11 and Vilgax have teamed up and have returned to earth to destroy Ben and get the Omnitrix.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: The Five Rules of Finding
description: Tiggy and Gweeseek use Chief's Five Rules of Finding to discover their own method of finding and locating Boss' missing tie.

title: Ben 10,000
description: Ben gets sucked into the future by a grown up Gwen. His mission is to help the now all powerful and adult Ben 10,000 seemingly defeat the future versions of Dr. Animo and Vilgax. However, the real reason Ben has been brought to the future is to teach his adult self some humility and the fact he's lost touch with Max and has forgotten what's really important, family.

title: The Good Lars
description: Steven, Lars and Sadie get invited to a party with the Cool Kids.

title: Pegado a Ti
description: Cansado de que Axel y el equipo lo den por sentado, Masko intenta ser secuestrado y termina atrapado en Dynamo, que está menos que entusiasmado con su nuevo compañero de goma.

title: Think Positive
description: Pops orders Benson to stop yelling at Mordecai and Rigby.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Crazy Day
description: It's Crazy Day again and Raven must do her best to avoid being driven crazy by the other Titans.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Jessica va al Arroyo
description: Cuando Craig y Jessica quedan encerrados fuera de la casa, Craig no tiene otra opción: debe llevar a su hermanita al Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Mouth Hole
description: Robin goes on a quest to gain a new power: whistling.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: Borrowed
description: Richard discovers his library books have been borrowed by Master Frown and sets off on a crazed mission to return the books before they're overdue.

title: Hose Water
description: When Cyborg and Starfire find a baby bird, it awakens their inner child.

title: Birthday Bash/Too Pooped to Puff
description: Birthday Bash: It's the girls birthday and some special presents have arrived from the girls' main enemies. Can they destroy these evil gifts without destroying their party?/Too Pooped to Puff: The girls become exhausted when the town begins to over use them. They go on strike and end up teaching the townspeople how to fend for themselves.

title: Chile libre
description: Cuando Owen oculta un walkie talky dentro de su perro con chile, Harold cree que es un alienígena que vino a destruir la tierra.

title: Un Aliado Peculiar
description: Lloyd se enfrenta a los Samurais Blizzard del Emperador de Hielo, pero es rescatado por un lobo extraño con quien desarrolla una amistad peculiar.

title: Deep Space Vacation
description: When Gar lets KO and Enid take a vacation to outer  space, they get more than they bargained for.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Transitional Phase
description: Life in the RV is interrupted when Uncle Grandpa and the gang keep mysteriously being sent back and forth through time.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Uncle Grandpa Babies
description: When the President calls in the Uncle Grandpa babies, they have to act quickly and use their special baby powers to defuse a missile.

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.

title: Stick Hockey
description: After Benson unjustifiably throws out Mordecai and Rigby's stick hockey table, he feels guilty and tries to help them get it back.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
